==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Piquet
<hw>Pi*quet"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., prob. fr.
<ets>pique</ets>. See <er>Pique</er>, <er>Pike</er>, and
<er>Picket</er>.]</ety> <def>A game at cards played between two persons,
with thirty-two cards, all the deuces, threes, fours, fives, and sixes,
being set aside.</def> <altsp>[Written also <asp>picket</asp> and
<asp>picquet</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Piracy</ent>⟦br⟧
